Package: libquenero9.2.0
Architecture: any
Depends: libminiupnpc17 (>= 2.1), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Quenero shared libraries
 This package contains the common Quenero library code used by the various Quenero
 binaries.

Package: libquenero-wallet9.2.0
Architecture: any
Depends: libquenero9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Quenero wallet shared libraries
 This package contains the common Quenero library code used by the various Quenero
 wallet-related code.

Package: quenerod
Architecture: any
Depends: libquenero9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, debconf
Suggests: quenero-blockchain-tools, quenero-wallet-cli
Description: Quenero network daemon
 This package contains the Quenero network daemon, quenerod, for running an Quenero node
 or Quenero service node.

Package: quenero-wallet-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: libquenero-wallet9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}), libquenero9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
    ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: quenerod
Description: Quenero command-line wallet and JSON RPC wallet
 This package contains the Quenero command-line wallet for accessing a wallet
 stored on the Quenero blockchain.
 .
 The wallets require a quenerod node to work, such as the one provided in the
 quenerod package, but can also work with a remote Quenero node.

Package: quenero-wallet-rpc
Architecture: any
Depends: libquenero-wallet9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}), libquenero9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
    ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: quenerod
Description: Quenero RPC wallet
 This package contains the Quenero JSON RPC wallet interface to accessing a wallet
 on the Quenero blockchain.  This wallet interface is typically used by external
 software that needs to interact with a wallet.
 .
 The wallet requires a quenerod node to work, such as the one provided in the
 quenerod package, but can also work with a remote Quenero node.

Package: quenero-blockchain-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: libquenero-wallet9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}), libquenero9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
    ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: quenerod
Description: Quenero blockchain utilities
 This contains the quenero-blockchain-* binaries for managing and querying the
 quenerod blockchain database.  These tools are used for blockchain diagnostics
 and are not typically needed to run an ordinary node or service node.

Package: libquenero-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libquenero-wallet9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}), libquenero9.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libboost-dev (>= 1.58), libboost-thread-dev, libboost-serialization-dev, libboost-program-options-dev,
 libunbound-dev (>= 1.4.16), libminiupnpc-dev, libssl-dev, libsodium-dev, libreadline-dev, libhidapi-dev, liboxenmq-dev (>= 1.2.3~),
 libsqlite3-dev, libcurl4-dev, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Quenero development files
 This contains the headers needed to compile code that uses the quenero libraries.
